lls, unlimited quizzes, per event up to 100 participants</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kahoot.com/\">Kahoot! - Learning games - Make learning awesome!</a> free for quizzes for 10 participants</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.poll-maker.com/\">Make a Poll in Seconds - Free &#x26; Unlimited - Poll Maker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://trypingo.com/\">PINGO‚ÄìPeer Instruction for very large Groups, Classroom-Response-System, Audience-Feedback</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learning-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#learning-tools\" aria-label=\"learning tools permalink\" class=\"toc-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Learning Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://padlet.com/dashboard\">Padlet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.techlearning.com/resources/free-online-learning-resources-for-schools-affected-by-coronaviruscovid-19\">Free Online Learning Resources For Back to School 2021 - Tech &#x26; Learning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://edu.google.com/teacher-center/certifications/educator-level1/?modal_active=none\">Educator Level 1 - Teacher Center - Google for Education</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://skillshop.exceedlms.com/student/path/61209-fundamentals-training\">Fundamentals Training : Google</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"education\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#education\" aria-label=\"education permalink\" class=\"toc-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4